com.fujitsu.xml.xbrl.inlinexbrl.generator
Interface InlineXBRLGeneratorErrorHandler

public interface InlineXBRLGeneratorErrorHandler

An interface that defines methods for reporting errors found while generating inline XBRL documents. Application programs can receive such errors and/or warnings by implementing this interface then registering it to the inline XBRL generator using InlineXBRLGenerator.setErrorHandler(InlineXBRLGeneratorErrorHandler).
